====== H2403: חַטָּאָה ======

===== Source =====

or   ; from  H2398 ;

===== Meaning =====

an  offence  (sometimes habitual sinfulness), and its  penalty ,  occasion ,  sacrifice , or  expiation ; also (concretely) an  offender

===== Definitions =====

  - offence
  - penalty
  - occasion
  - sacrifice
  - expiation
  - offender

===== Usage =====

punishment (of sin), purifying(-fication for sin), sin(-ner, offering).
